I believed Amber. I saw the bruise, then the mirror ‘easy Amber’ etc. Why did I believe her? Because usually, it’s true. False reports are more rare. He was a beloved actor, why would she lie? Then she came out and said she would give away ALL THE MONEY. I’m a survivor of a violent sexual assault. I believed her.

It terrifies me how easily I was manipulated. I couldn’t believe it when I watched the full video of her. How anyone can be that evil is beyond me

I don’t think ERW and Amber are the same from all the research I’ve done. But I think Amber is a psychopath. Anyone who had been through domestic violence or physical or sexual assault will feel so much revulsion that people could fabricate this.

It’s not on Evan to call Amber a liar though?? I mean come on. Do I really need to explain that to you? You’re not a 25 year old, I think you must have enough experience to do deeper more logical takes?
